{"tid":1352290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句 選擇跳樓死既人唔值得稱為烈士","createTime":"2019-07-22T18:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T19:10:46.000Z","uid":6647,"like":59,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c5648a42eb3db7deeb376952e25aae2aa9488194","tid":1352290,"uid":6647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:18:21.000Z","msg":"今日又一單...<br />\n我知經過721香港又更黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係可唔可以唔好再選擇跳樓<br />\n亦都唔好再吹奏跳樓<br />\n因為跟本冇助成個運動<br />\n而且間直地宣揚跳樓=英雄化<br />\n頭一兩個, okay, make到noise<br />\n但之後個D真係唔值得<br />\n<br />\n你都有自殺既勇氣<br />\n點解冇做勇武既勇氣？<br />\n<br />\n純分享歷史，唔係鼓吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-VhLrGY_SXdM/XLRWb8Dr4LI/AAAAAAAA2EM/Gh_JaYFtv2sa-jfEc85nLlLlyrDb-YS-ACLcBGAs/s1600/08_anime.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-VhLrGY_SXdM%2FXLRWb8Dr4LI%2FAAAAAAAA2EM%2FGh_JaYFtv2sa-jfEc85nLlLlyrDb-YS-ACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F08_anime.jpg&h=315e22b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lGmWBfo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlGmWBfo.gif&h=ce86dfd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，我絕對唔贊成犧牲自己，生命可貴。<br />\n請一齊行到最後"},{"pid":"7c47bf4103371ba2fbc861505ccbacd2eb1d73c7","tid":1352290,"uid":144849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:20:05.000Z","msg":"尊重"},{"pid":"9d28a02aba1e1d34c03b4d3dd7817e3315d2ab61","tid":1352290,"uid":6647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:22:59.000Z","msg":"重申，以上純粹係我自己見解，唔鼓吹任何野。<br />\n<br />\n最後，RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcff60fcdd6acb4ecd612d950f62ef10bd2cf69","tid":1352290,"uid":6647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:25:15.000Z","msg":"唔值得!"},{"pid":"3068c8c5c46eb14d59aed0ed749e86af2f2c4732","tid":1352290,"uid":182